title: Gorgeous Oakland Hills house for rent - A MUST SEE HOUSE!
posting_body: ['3 bed/2 bath home in Montclair Hills - 6601 Oakwood Drive, Oakland.', 'Ever wished to live in the Montclair Hills?', 'Now is your chance!', 'Sunny 3 bed/2 bath traditional home in the safest neighborhood in Oakland!', 'Nestled in the Montclair hills yet only blocks away from Montclair village, Hwy 13, and transbay bus line.', 'Take advantage of highly rated Montclair elementary schools and enjoy a drive to all the wonderful restaurants, shopping, and Sunday farmers market Montclair Village has to offer.', '1 inside garage space, 1 drive way space, and street parking availability 24/7!', 'Large flat terrace will inspire many ideas to make this Oasis your own.', "This home is perfect for watching the sunset or planting that vegetable garden you've always wanted to.", 'Details:', 'Bedrooms: 3', 'Bathrooms: 2', 'Term: 12 Months', 'Monthly Rent $5950', 'Security Deposit: $5950', 'Laundry:', 'In-unit', 'Parking: 1 car garage, driveway, and street', 'Pets:', 'Yes, small cats or small dog with additional deposit ($100/month)', 'Utilities: Water, garbage, electric tenant responsibility.', 'DATE AVAILABLE: 8/31/2022!', 'Items needed when submitting an application:', '*', "Last year's W2, or tax return if you are self-employed", '* Two current pay stubs', "* Most recent two month's bank statements", "* A copy of Driver's License or ID", '*Rental terms subject to change or amendments', '*Rental requirements include (but are not limited to): Monthly income must be at least 3x the rent (or 3x the tenant portion if on Section 8), 700 FICO score or better, no evictions']
